"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Iranian state media claimed something after Donald Trump said the US military would help free commercial ships stuck around a key waterway. This comes as Russia plans a smaller military parade. There have been deaths in Ukraine, and Kyiv says Russian tankers were hit by drones.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran, Trump, and Russia\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los medios de Ir\u00e1n dijeron algo despu\u00e9s de que Donald Trump dijo que el ej\u00e9rcito de EE.UU. ayudar\u00eda a liberar barcos comerciales atrapados en un canal importante. Esto pasa mientras Rusia planea un desfile militar m\u00e1s peque\u00f1o. Ha habido muertes en Ucrania, y Kyiv dice que drones golpearon barcos rusos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ir\u00e1n, Trump y Rusia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Peter Obi and Rabiu Kwankwaso, who came third and fourth in the last elections, have changed their political parties.\",            \"english_title\": \"Politicians Change Parties\",            \"translated_version\": \"Peter Obi y Rabiu Kwankwaso, que quedaron tercero y cuarto en las \u00faltimas elecciones, han cambiado de partidos pol\u00edticos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pol\u00edticos cambian de partido\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The World Health Organization reported one confirmed case of hantavirus infection, with five more cases being investigated.\",            \"english_title\": \"Hantavirus Case Reported\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Organizaci\u00f3n Mundial de la Salud inform\u00f3 un caso confirmado de infecci\u00f3n por hantavirus, con cinco casos m\u00e1s siendo investigados.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Caso de hantavirus reportado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A long-time supporter of Trump and former New York mayor is in the hospital, according to his spokesman.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump Supporter Hospitalized\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un seguidor de Trump y exalcalde de Nueva York est\u00e1 en el hospital, seg\u00fan su portavoz.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Seguidor de Trump hospitalizado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two European summits are happening in a country that has been a close ally of Russia in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"European Summits in Ally Country\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos cumbres europeas est\u00e1n ocurriendo en un pa\u00eds que ha sido un aliado cercano de Rusia en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cumbres europeas en pa\u00eds aliado\"        }    ]}"